Blacknightamare:The femme smiled and said "I'm not tired"
Malice:  "Aww.  Well is it okay if you still si here, just for my 
sake?"
Blacknightamre: the femme laughted softly and said "If you want... 
I'll remaind here"
Malice:  The male laughed a little and hugged Blacknightmare close, 
trying to mak the best of it.  Their happiness may be shortlived.  
He rested his head on her shoulder and shut off his optics, but did 
not go to sleep, as he had many things on his mind.
Blacknightamre: the femme smiled and glenty she touched him, she 
tought that he really was sleeping so she don't try to disturb
Malice:  Malice quietly rested, thinking of what exactly to do when 
it came time to go back to the Maximal Base.  He'd have to hammer 
out a deal so Blacknightmare could stay, and find a way so Wolfblade 
didn't ream him when he finally returned.  Such choices.  He sighed 
heavily and decided to rest, enjoying being so close o 
Blacknightmare.
Blacknightmare: the femme also was meditating, would she and her sis 
welcomed to Maximal base? if they wouldn't, where they would go?
Malice:  The bounty hunter also thought of what to do with 
Hellplague.  She was more likely to not go with them, she would 
rather live without the Maximals and live alone.  That made him a 
litle sad, but it was her choice, not his.  Malice settled down and 
readied to go to sleep this time.
Blacknightmare: Blacknightmare continued meditating.
